title: Excel Decoder Agent Transaction Behavior - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
text: Transaction Behavior This section includes information about the Decompressor agent's transaction behavior. For information about the general transaction behavior, see 3.1.11 Workflow Monitor . Emits The Excel Decoder agent does not emit any commands. Retrieves The Excel Decoder agent does not retrieve any commands.
